                            <li class="active">
                                <i class="fa fa-dashboard"></i> Overview
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                        <h4>This chart shows the energy useage of your system. The vertical axis is kilowatt-hours, and the horizontal axis is time. Data collected from your system is aggregated daily and added to this chart. <br>
                    </div>
