                                        <i class="fa fa-dashboard"></i> Information
                                    </li>
                                </ol>
                                <h4>Each luminaire (lighting fixture) of the Luminesense system has a wattage of 12. By tracking how many of these are on or off over a period of time, we can track energy useage. The lower this number, the better!</h4>
